<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title><%= @organization.name %> - Presentation Delivery</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .attachment-notice {
      background: #f0f8ff;
      border: 1px solid #c7e3ff;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1><%= @organization.name %></h1>
    <p>Presentation Delivery</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello <%= @user.first_name || @user.email %>,</p>
    
    <p><%= simple_format(@body) %></p>
    
    <div class="attachment-notice">
      <h3>🎁 Presentation Delivered</h3>
      <p>Your presentation file has been attached to this email. Please download the attachment to access your presentation materials.</p>
      <p><strong>Note:</strong> This file has been securely validated and is safe to download.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p><strong>Delivered:</strong> <%= Time.current.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p %Z') %></p>
    <p>This presentation was delivered by the Data Refinery Platform.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions or issues accessing the presentation, please contact your system administrator.</p>
    
    <hr>
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
      <%= @organization.name %> | Data Refinery Platform<br>
      You received this email because you requested this presentation delivery.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>